{"tid":828406,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"we are 中大精英","createTime":"2018-09-19T15:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T03:52:00.000Z","uid":205339,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4b5cc31a9b7087469828a1acf84746eef076037d","tid":828406,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T15:56:18.000Z","msg":"We are stem guy.<br />\n無3322都唔撚驚<br />\n直入中大science engineering<br />\n俾一眾斷手斷腳既大陸仔感受中大馬場濃厚鄉村氣息<br />\n仲有東鐵綫既新鮮抗藥性惡菌<br />\nMe 117(7)177<br />\nWe are stem!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f42cf40ecbe8cc59a2b474dc4e871d86696278d","tid":828406,"uid":132968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T15:56:57.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"36840e4d894304ec01cc82da81a4a23b42be8eca","tid":828406,"uid":205339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T16:01:01.000Z","msg":"中文大學理學院及工程學院，2019/2020學年推出「特別入學考慮措施」。未達大學入學門檻考生，若STEM（科學、科技、工程和數學）表現優良，仍有機會獲中大取錄。<br />\n<br />\n報讀中大理學院和工程學院任何學科的考生，若在3個STEM類文憑試科（物理、化學、生物、數學延伸單元一或二、資訊及通訊科技、設計與應用科技、組合科學及綜合科學）之中，取得3粒星，即3科都有5*，或1科5*、另一科5**，同時在大學聯招將學科放較前志願。這類考生即使在DSE的4個核心科（中英數、通識教育）未達入大學最低要求「3322」，仍會獲特別考慮，包括予以面試機會。<br />\n<br />\n中大副校長（教育）潘偉賢認為，對修讀理學院或工程學院的學生，STEM能力比一般能力更重要，盼吸納STEM能力「既廣且深」的學生，而非只側重個別一科。她又稱，中國投入科研的經費與年俱增，要使香港成為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大灣區</span></span>內，甚至世界科技發展先驅，必須把握時機，故此中大將以培育STEM人才為未來中其中一個教育方向。<br />\n<br />\n中大協理副校長王淑英強調，校方絕非否定4個核心科目的入學要求，仍然鼓勵學生要讀好4個核心科，但亦希望向STEM學科出色又有熱誠的學生，予以入學機會。中大理學院副院長（學生事務）王海嬰稱，盼此舉能鼓勵對STEM具熱誠的中學生，在中四揀選修科時「集中火力」選STEM科。"},{"pid":"aed597d01ffa81bc9ca6ce82b9a6f7eefd5aa237","tid":828406,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T16:04:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">greater bay area</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207c2d433952ccef9f0382d03e3ccd46f4d77a82","tid":828406,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T17:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f218988cc1528a1439edcd22f8ffe9ea135cbb","tid":828406,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60dc742c1b48d4d9019774f84f22b9fdb3dbd6c","tid":828406,"uid":175598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:33:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf5911600bc1be492f9ab834567d309ae4cadbd0","tid":828406,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b60dc742c1b48d4d9019774f84f22b9fdb3dbd6c","tid":828406,"uid":175598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:33:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:36:13.000Z","msg":"Chinese u單係個朵都勁過你啦<br />\n大灣區第一學苑<br />\n你睇下Chinese u chi-na 分校運作得幾順暢<br />\n一車車中大人(nds) 運哂入去"},{"pid":"8d491c48e6f7cf88a0acb41c9b0e4b264391b82d","tid":828406,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf5911600bc1be492f9ab834567d309ae4cadbd0","tid":828406,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b60dc742c1b48d4d9019774f84f22b9fdb3dbd6c","tid":828406,"uid":175598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:33:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:36:13.000Z","msg":"Chinese u單係個朵都勁過你啦<br />\n大灣區第一學苑<br />\n你睇下Chinese u chi-na 分校運作得幾順暢<br />\n一車車中大人(nds) 運哂入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:36:53.000Z","msg":"我港大都屌打你"},{"pid":"643c30e56f3633059dc62ff2900b884c2e687384","tid":828406,"uid":135445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T02:38:54.000Z","msg":"好過收堆22 21分既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"